strings: <voice_0x01000C40><se_def>China: I know you said that before the funeral. However, I want everyone to know that you are innocent.
<voice_0x01000C41><se_def>China: If it hadn't been for you, Captain Marcello might have died.
<voice_0x01000C42><se_def>China: ...Nevertheless, the templar called you to his office.
<voice_0x01000C43><se_def>China: Until we meet again, please remember!
